
======================================================================
EXEC-REMOTE Fetches and runs external code [CRITICAL]
======================================================================

Category:
  Malicious Code  (detector: remote_exec)

Description:
  The package downloads and executes code from an external URL at
  build/install time; the scanner does not follow it (opaque
  boundary).

Recommendation:
  Do not build; obtain software that ships its real code.

CWE: CWE-494

======================================================================
